    "Name": "Legionnaire",
    "Details": "A project to create an upgrade package for the Legionnaire, developed under the supervision of Sandra Hall-Pujanauski, this version carries an ER medium laser in each arm. The standard armor was replaced by Clan made reflective armor, and a Clan built RAC/5 was crammed into the right torso. To provide room for the pilot, the MUSE FIRE uses a torso-mounted cockpit, and the room freed in the 'Mech's head is used to store three tons of ammunition. This version doesn't carry the targeting computer of the standard version.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Improved Targeting - Medium</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.09</color></b>",
